&gt; Tails:Yeah, I hate it.
&gt; Sonic:Ok, I'll call you something else, I'll call you Tails.
&gt; Tails:Wow, what a day, I find out that I'm not a bird, not a bug, get a brother, and get a new name, I'm Tails!
&gt; Sonic:(barely holding on to the net as Tails is flying around really quickly)
